{"tid":1373734,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"見證 電子支付 指紋 face id 唔完全識合香港用","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:49:14.000Z","uid":113000,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed054b9099755d2447aa1aace2f1f55d317e6910","tid":1373734,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"大家以為自己係住美國歐洲咁有人權真係諗多左<br />\n<br />\n用還用 現金 密碼還是冇可取替<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「老豆搵仔」admin被捕 被控合謀及教唆謀殺<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373059/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373059/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》刊出一篇題為&quot;In Hong Kong Protests, Faces Become Weapons&quot;的專訪，透露Colin Cheung保釋後，仍然被便衣探員跟蹤，幾經辛苦才擺脫成功跟紐時記者會面。他回憶在7月18日在一商場被四名沒有出示警員委任證的便衣人員捉走，在車上四人又掌摑又扯頭，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘗試用Colin的臉解開其手機，但最終都不成功。後來他被帶至警署，被嚴刑逼供，警方又到其住所，用黑客程序入侵其電腦搜證</span></span>，被捕過程超過10小時，但最後未被任何罪名起訴下保釋。"},{"pid":"34028321932f3c8ff2fc61f1beaca6d4232c83c6","tid":1373734,"uid":39860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"警犬可恥"},{"pid":"77a5b0914febd749fa0fe574c0105af7fcb22918","tid":1373734,"uid":89514,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33091f0cb169e5056cbb1ddae58ea0fadb331881","tid":1373734,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"77a5b0914febd749fa0fe574c0105af7fcb22918","tid":1373734,"uid":89514,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"iphone先係<br />\n<br />\nandroid pixel好似冇"},{"pid":"256ed21462e02f60f02df057e1ccfae013c05bae","tid":1373734,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e962887c07c5f41dfeb66a5312a2c9efdd1d932","tid":1373734,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2